HEADWORD: Sulpho-
<hw>Sul"pho-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A prefix (also
used adjectively) designating <xex>sulphur as an ingredient</xex> in
certain compounds. Cf. <er>Thio-</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

